---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Contact Hummingbird Social Studio | Wedding Template Questions" 
  description="Contact Hummingbird Social Studio with questions about editable wedding templates, invitation suites, bridal shower invitations, and custom stationery ideas."
>
  <main>

    <section class="page-hero">
      <div class="container content">
        <p class="eyebrow">Contact</p>

        <h1>Have a question or custom idea?</h1>

        <p class="lead">
          Reach out with questions about wedding templates, invitation suites,
          bridal shower invitations, matching stationery, downloadable designs,
          or future custom wedding projects.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container content">

        <h2>Get in Touch</h2>

        <p>
          We would love to hear from you. Whether you are looking for help choosing
          a wedding invitation suite, need support with a downloadable template,
          or want to discuss a custom design idea, feel free to reach out anytime.
        </p>

        <p>
          Hummingbird Social Studio focuses on timeless, modern, and stylish wedding
          stationery inspired by minimalist, editorial, mid-century modern,
          black and white, and destination wedding aesthetics.
        </p>

        <p>
          <a class="button" href="mailto:gradualgrowthonline@gmail.com">
            Email Hummingbird Social Studio
          </a>
        </p>

        <p>
          You can also reach out for questions about wedding invitation customization,
          matching stationery pieces, bridal shower invitations, save the dates,
          wedding signage, and downloadable wedding templates.
        </p>

      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>
